<font size="20">♪A flower blooms alone
amidst the thorns♪</font>

9
00:00:41,920 --> 00:00:44,160
<font size="20">♪its petals pierced by thorns♪</font>

10
00:00:44,380 --> 00:00:49,080
<font size="20">♪Yet it turned into a pair of wings
flying against the wind♪</font>

11
