<font size="20">can barely walk now.</font>

719
00:42:09,280 --> 00:42:10,760
<font size="20">Come on, let's get in.</font>

720
00:42:24,520 --> 00:42:25,560
<font size="20">Let alone a bed,</font>

721
00:42:26,160 --> 00:42:27,440
<font size="20">there isn't even a blanket here.</font>

722
00:42:28,000 --> 00:42:28,600
<font size="20">Yeah,</font>

723
00:42:29,000 --> 00:42:29,920
<font size="20">we have nothing here.</font>

724
00:42:29,960 --> 00:42:30,680
<font size="20">How are we gonna live in this place?</font>

725
00:42:30,960 --> 00:42:32,680
<font size="20">This is not a place for human.</font>

726
