<font size="20">You can take my room then.</font>

727
00:42:41,200 --> 00:42:43,400
<font size="20">We can sleep anywhere.</font>

728
00:42:44,000 --> 00:42:45,600
<font size="20">Madam, don't worry.</font>

729
00:42:45,840 --> 00:42:46,440
<font size="20">Don't worry.</font>

